Term and Termination
Subject to Article 22.2, this Agreement shall remain in force for an Initial Period of 1 year, which may be renewed by mutual consent for such period as the Parties may agree ("Term"), unless it is terminated earlier in accordance with this Agreement or for any of the following reasons:
if one Party is in default with its performance under this Agreement;
in case of insolvency or bankruptcy of either Party, or in case of a change of control of one of the Parties;
breach of any of the provisions of this Agreement by either Party that remains unremedied for a period of 30 days;

